title: Percentage of childless women , by age U.S. 2018
summary: Overall Percentage of childless women has increased over the Year.
Percentage of childless women is slightly increasing from 40_to_44_years_old to 45_to_50_years_old.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 40_to_44_years_old and 45_to_50_years_old.
The highest Percentage of childless women, of value 15.4 was reached at Year 45_to_50_years_old
Minimum Percentage of childless women about 15.0 was reached at Year 40_to_44_years_old
